 : \"1.0-alpha-2\",\n    \"source-code-url\" : \"https://github.com/codehaus-plexus/plexus-utils/tree/1950721c6b6a68a79c5faf0da9264342299360b5/src/main/java\",\n    \"repository-url\" : \"https://github.com/codehaus-plexus/plexus-utils\",\n    \"test-code-url\" : \"https://github.com/codehaus-plexus/plexus-utils/tree/1950721c6b6a68a79c5faf0da9264342299360b5/src/test/java\",\n    \"documentation-url\" : \"https://javadoc.io/doc/plexus/plexus-utils/$version$\",\n    \"description\" : \"Plexus Utils provides common Java utility classes historically used by Maven and Plexus-based projects. It includes helpers for file and IO handling, string manipulation, command-line execution, directory scanning, graph processing, reflection and introspection, and XML utilities.\",\n    \"tested-versions\" : [\n      \"1.0-alpha-2\"\n    ],\n    \"allowed-packages\" : [\n      \"org.codehaus.plexus.util\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    \"metadata-version\" : \"1.0-alpha-1\",\n    \"source-code-url\" : \"https://github.com/codehaus-plexus/plexus-utils/tree/de2f71c9b2437b4d82ad635c30ec69370adf0033/src/main/java\",\n    \"repository-url\" : \"https://github.com/codehaus-plexus/plexus-utils\",\n    \"test-code-url\" : \"https://github.com/codehaus-plexus/plexus-utils/tree/de2f71c9b2437b4d82ad635c30ec69370adf0033/src/test/java\",\n    \"documentation-url\" : \"https://javadoc.io/doc/plexus/plexus-utils/$version$\",\n    \"description\" : \"Plexus Utils provides common Java utilities historically used by Apache Maven and Plexus-based projects. It includes helpers for file and IO handling, string manipulation, command-line execution, DAG processing, introspection, and XML utilities.\",\n    \"tested-versions\" : [\n      \"1.0-alpha-1\"\n    ],\n    \"allowed-packages\" : [\n      \"org.codehaus.plexus.util\"\n    ]\n  }\n]\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1782478827025}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_nyqjSH4SbFtHqyGgR3T7nmDV|fc_0d96c9b578fa339c016a3e77ead12481939992e475469424c7", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\npackage plexus.plexus_utils;\n\nimport java.lang.reflect.Field;\nimport java.lang.reflect.Method;\n\nimport org.codehaus.plexus.util.ReflectionUtils;\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n\nimport static org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThat;\n\npublic class ReflectionUtilsTest {\n    @Test\n    void findsFieldsDeclaredOnSuperclasses() {\n        Field field = ReflectionUtils.getFieldByNameIncludingSuperclasses(\"inheritedValue\", ChildBean.class);\n\n        assertThat(field).isNotNull();\n        assertThat(field.getName()).isEqualTo(\"inheritedValue\");\n        assertThat(field.getDeclaringClass()).isEqualTo(ParentBean.class);\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void findsPublicVoidInstanceSetter() {\n        Method setter = ReflectionUtils.getSetter(\"name\", ChildBean.class);\n\n        assertThat(setter).isNotNull();\n        assertThat(setter.getName()).isEqualTo(\"setName\");\n        assertThat(setter.getReturnType()).isEqualTo(Void.TYPE);\n        assertThat(setter.getParameterTypes()).containsExactly(String.class);\n    }\n\n    public static class ParentBean {\n        public String inheritedValue;\n    }\n\n    public static class ChildBean extends ParentBean {\n        public void setName(String name) {\n            inheritedValue = name;\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1782478827025}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_jnOXv6zNFMtY7JRaEoAgi15S|fc_0d96c9b578fa339c016a3e77ead1288193bfd9d6d2f83e32c4", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"fix_javac_fail:2026-06-06\": {\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-06-06T20:38:29.561304Z\",\n    \"library\": \"plexus:plexus-utils:1.0-alpha-2\",\n    \"starting_commit\": \"4c542f0b018f027e6e55445b25485bc2953cd